   "source": [
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "bce0d6a3-5799-4af5-b074-ca7add6c057f",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Plots"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "ec26849f-0008-44ad-a7b5-4b418b384e2f",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Scatter Plot"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "id": "ac6e2faf-a3b2-44cb-830c-e0b2d7966f8b",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "sns.scatterplot(x=..., y=..., hue = ..., size = ...)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "f6edf703-abf1-4371-bbb7-bae5a89cea9e",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Count Plot (Bar Chart)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "id": "b3cc5990-8d08-4abc-bd40-637949817f0a",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "sns.countplot(x=categories) [or sns.countplot(y=categories)] -> If you specify x, you get a vertical bar chart. Specify y, it's horizontal\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "bbbf4138-505d-4dae-80b1-79b546a53f94",
